	  &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-compiler-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;
	  &lt;version&gt;3.6.1&lt;/version&gt;
	  &lt;configuration&gt;
		&lt;source&gt;1.6&lt;/source&gt;
		&lt;target&gt;1.6&lt;/target&gt;
	  &lt;/configuration&gt;
  	&lt;/plugin&gt;

For more info check these links:

[maven compiler][1]

[bug report][2]


